Calculate MAP-PI-PlGF Joint Distribution

get_p_MAP_PI_PlGF.Rd

Calculates the joint probability distribution for MAP, PI, and PlGF MoM values

Usage

get_p_MAP_PI_PlGF(mom_MAP, mom_PI, mom_PlGF, g)

Arguments

mom_MAP

Numeric, MAP MoM value

mom_PI

Numeric, PI MoM value

mom_PlGF

Numeric, PlGF MoM value

g

Numeric vector, gestational ages

Value

Numeric vector of probability densities
